text: Nurul Islam Chowdhury is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-11. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Chittagong-11 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
